sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Gateway
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Sidecar as llm-d-routing-sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Allowlist as AllowlistValidator<br/>(in-process)
    participant Prefiller as Remote vLLM Prefiller<br/>variable port HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Decoder as Local vLLM Decoder<br/>8001/TCP HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (NIXL v2)

    Client->>Route: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Header: x-prefiller-host-port: <host>:<port>
    Route->>Sidecar: Forward (TLS edge termination)

    Sidecar->>Allowlist: Validate prefiller target host
    Allowlist-->>Sidecar: Approved (host in InferencePool pod list)

    Note over Sidecar: Wrap request with kv_transfer_params<br/>Set max_tokens=1, stream=false<br/>Add remote_prefill=true, engine_id

    Sidecar->>Prefiller: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Modified request (prefill phase)<br/>Optional TLS 1.2+
    Prefiller-->>Sidecar: Prefill response<br/>Contains: block_ids, engine_id,<br/>host, port for KV transfer

    Note over Sidecar: Extract kv_transfer_params from response<br/>Construct decode request with<br/>remote_decode=true + prefill params

    Sidecar->>Decoder: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Decode request with kv_transfer_params<br/>Optional TLS 1.2+
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Streaming decode response
    Sidecar-->>Route: Stream response
    Route-->>Client: Streaming HTTPS response

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Direct Passthrough (No Prefill Header)

    Client->>Route: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(no x-prefiller-host-port header)
    Route->>Sidecar: Forward (TLS edge termination)

    Note over Sidecar: No prefill header detected<br/>Direct reverse proxy passthrough

    Sidecar->>Decoder: Forward original request<br/>8001/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Response
    Sidecar-->>Route: Forward response
    Route-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,Decoder: Background: SSRF Allowlist Maintenance

    loop Kubernetes Watch (continuous)
        Allowlist->>Allowlist: Watch InferencePool CR<br/>(inference.networking.x-k8s.io/v1alpha2)
        Note over Allowlist: Rebuild allowlist from<br/>pod IPs matching pool selector
    end
